<p id="fs-idm69273568">A table of ionization constants for weak bases appears in <a class="target-chapter" href="i-ionization-constants-of-weak-bases">Appendix I</a>. As for acids, the relative strength of a base is also reflected in its percent ionization, computed as</p>
